original_title: AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2012
overview: The AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2012 (AKB48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト100 2012) was held from January 19 to January 22, 2012 at Tokyo Dome City Hall. Fans made their voices heard by voting for their favorite AKB48/SKE48/NMB48/SDN48 original songs.
title: AKB48 Request Hour Setlist Best 100 2012
